4828S01.08S
220 5. There shall be added to or subtracted from the
221 taxpayer's federal adjusted gross income the modifications
222 provided in section 143.411.
223 6. In addition to the modifications to a taxpayer's
224 federal adjusted gross income in this section, to calculate
225 Missouri adjusted gross income there shall be subtracted
226 from the taxpayer's federal adjusted gross income any gain
227 recognized pursuant to 26 U.S.C. Section 1033 of the
228 Internal Revenue Code of 1986, as amended, arising from
229 compulsory or involuntary conversion of property as a result
